title: On-Camera Commercial Intensive with CD Rachel Reiss of Liz Lewis Casting
desc: Get on-camera coaching to help on your next commercial audition. Actors can bring their own copy, select from the commercial copy database on the home page, or Rachel will bring copy for you to work with. This class is for actor ages 18+ Work with Rachel one-on-one in this classroom setting to hone your commercial audition technique. Let an experienced CD help you improve your technique and book more work. Your footage will be uploaded to you private profile for review and download.
